Summary: A series of affects occurred for me to spot a UFO.
trends: There have been 15 other sightings in Moose Jaw
There were no other sightings in Moose Jaw on or around January 6th 2011
divs: sighting detailsfeeling down or sad, the phone rang and i felt the need to open the door and look up at one region of the sky and i spotted a ufo heading southbound. thereafter, i felt instantly gratified and thankful because, i think the ufo visitations offer me a sense of security, peace of mind and understanding. i'm usually either emotional or feeling selfless when these sightings come to my attention or get an urge to "look up" because, i literally "feel" something is up there. i was thinking about time travel, men in black, the future and the past. i also was feeling annoyed about how it's winter and i rarely get the chance to observe the night sky to potentially encounter ufos. longing for spring\summer to come. wondering if i'd get another sighting. so by law of attraction or intelligent design, one came for me to see... that's my interpretation.
